  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Associate of \u201cKudu Salindu\u201d arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); One of the main associates of Salidu alias Panadura \"Kudu Salidu\" who is involved in many organized crimes and large-scale drug trafficking has been arrested.",
        "Accordingly, police said that a 40-year-old man who was in possession of a sword with intent to commit murder was arrested in Wadduwa area.",
        "The arrested suspect was identified as a person who has been previously convicted of possessing a live grenade and has been fined by the court and was subsequently released on bail.",
        "He is also a suspect who has been released on bail after being imprisoned for killing a person by firing a T-56 firearm.",
        "The police said that he was previously incarcerated for possession of heroin and various charges and was last released on bail about 02 months ago.",
        "China says it will support consultations for SL debt solution"
      ],
